#@NAME       : NUestimate_np_and_em
#@INPUT      : 
#@OUTPUT     : 
#@RETURNS    : 
#@DESCRIPTION: iteratively estimates intensity non-uniformity artifacts
#@              in MRI volumes
#@METHOD     : 
#@GLOBALS    : 
#@CALLS      : 
#@CREATED    : January 15, 1996      J.G.Sled  
#@MODIFIED   : 
